1. *Zadovoljstvom* mogu reći da smo uspešno realizovali projekat. (With *satisfaction*, I can say that we successfully completed the project.)
2. Bilo mi je *zadovoljstvo* raditi s vama. (*Pleasure* working with you.)
3. Naša kompanija je *zadovoljstvom* primila vašu ponudu. (Our company *received with pleasure* your offer.)
4. *Zadovoljstvo* nam je da vas pozovemo na naš događaj. (It's our *pleasure* to invite you to our event.)
5. Radujem se s *zadovoljstvom* vašem dolasku. (I look forward to your arrival *with pleasure*.)
6. Poklon je primila s velikim *zadovoljstvom*. (She received the gift with great *satisfaction*.)
7. Uspeli smo da ostvarimo svoje ciljeve s *zadovoljstvom*. (We were able to achieve our goals *with satisfaction*.)
8. Izrazio je *zadovoljstvo* kada je čuo vesti. (He expressed *satisfaction* when he heard the news.)
9. *Zadovoljstvom* obaveštavamo naše klijente o novim proizvodima. (We *are pleased to inform* our clients about our new products.)
10. Kupci su izrazili svoje *zadovoljstvo* kvalitetom proizvoda. (The customers expressed their *satisfaction* with the quality of the products.)